52
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,640
 nema mjesta

53
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:15,020
 nikakvoj depresiji

54
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:16,280
 ni anksioznosti

55
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:19,200
